<P>THE RELIEF, OR, DAY THOUGHTS: A POEM.</P>
<P>OCCASIONED BY THE <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">OMPLAINT, OR NIGHT THOUGHTS.</P>
<P>Humbly In&s;cribed to The RIGHT HONOURABLE The EARL of HOLDERNESS.</P>
<Q><L>&mdash;A&s;&s;ert Eternal Providence,</L>
<L>And ju&s;tify the Ways of God to Men.</L>
<BIBL>MILTON.</BIBL></Q>
<P>LONDON: Printed in the Year M.DCC.LIV.</P>
